<%= fb_title 'About' %>

<div id='ibm-logo' align='left'>
  <br/>
  <%= link_to image_tag('people_finder.jpg', :border => 0, :size => '50x75'), '#{people_finder_url}' %>
</div>

<h2>About <%= app_name %></h2>
<p><%= site_blurb %></p>

<table border='0'>
<tr>
<td>
<div id='twitter' align='left'>
  Follow us on <a href='<%= people_finder_twitter_url %>'>twitter</a> to get live updates of existing survivors and victims as well as newly added entries in order to help send relief faster.
  <p>
  <%= link_to image_tag('twitter_logo.png', :border => 0, :size => '160x43'), "#{people_finder_twitter_url}" %>
  </p>
</div>
</td>
<td>
<div align='google-maps' align='left'>
  Now you can get a <a href='http://maps.google.com'>Google Map</a> view of each <%= link_to 'location', :controller => 'locations', :action => 'index' %> with a marker with details survivors and victims information.  We also have a map with <%= link_to 'all locations', :controller => 'locations', :action => 'show_all_locations' %> and associated markers.
  <p>
  <%= link_to image_tag('google_maps_logo.png', :border => 0, :size => '173x41'), :controller => 'locations', :action => 'show_all_locations' %>
  </p>
</div>
</td>
</table>

<p>
<%= feedback_help_blurb %>
Here is our list of <%= link_to "Frequently Asked Questions", :controller => 'welcome', :action => 'faq' %> and the <%= link_to 'latest news', :controller => 'welcome', :action => 'news' %>.
<%= link_to "Contact Information", :controller => 'welcome',
                                      :action => 'contact' %>.
Please note that by using <%= app_name %> you are agreeing to its <%= link_to 'terms of use', :controller => 'welcome', :action => 'tou' %> and its <%= link_to 'privacy policy', :controller => 'welcome', :action => 'privacy_policy' %>.
</p>

<small>
<div align='right'>
  <%= link_to image_tag('ibm_arc_logo.jpg', :border => 0, :size => '100x42'), 'http://www.almaden.ibm.com' %>
  <br/>
  Version <%= version %>
</div>
</small>

<small>
<div align='center'>
Copyright 2010 &copy;  <a href='http://maximilien.org' alt='Maximilien'>E.M. Maximilien</a>
</div>
</small>

<hr/>

<div id='google-person-finder' align='center'>
<p>
Now all data in <%= link_to "#{app_name}", :controller => 'welcome', :action => 'index' %> are periodically sync with <a href='<%= google_person_finder %>'>Google Person Finder</a> which maintains a centralized DB of all similar applications involved in the Haiti Relief effort, e.g., <a href='http://www.ireport.com/ir-topic-stories.jspa?topicId=381628'>CNN's iReport</a>.
</p>
<div id='google-person-finder-iframe' align='center'>
<iframe
      src="<%= google_person_finder %>?small=yes"
      width=375 height=230 frameborder=0
      style="border: dashed 2px #77c">
</iframe>
</div>
</div>

<hr/>

<fb:feed max='<%= "#{max_news_feed_items}" %>'/>